This is a barebones, minimalistic app.
What is included are:
    a) Setup for sugarOrm - For a simple database layer
    b) Retrofit - To make REST calls
    c) Robolectric - Powerful unit test framework built to work with junit
    d) Butterknife - Android component dependency injection framework

To start:
0) get android studio
1) download android SDK 21 through the SDK manager.
2) Follow the instructions for editing the test configuration: http://robolectric.org/getting-started/
3) click build variants in the lower left hand side of android studio and select unit tests in the test artifact dropdown
4) Enjoy

